net.sf.jguiraffe.di.impl

Class AbstractInvocationTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.jguiraffe.di.impl.AbstractInvocationTest
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    TestConstructorInvocation, TestMethodInvocation

    public abstract class AbstractInvocationTest
extends Object
    An abstract base class for testing Invocation objects. This class defines some tests for the basic functionality provided by the Invocation base class. These tests are run on concrete implementations. Some useful constants are also provided.
    Version:
    $Id: AbstractInvocationTest.java 207 2012-02-09 07:30:13Z oheger $
    Author:
    Oliver Heger
